  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large skillet, cook the pork shoulder over medium high heat until browned.",
    "Add the onion, carrot, and celery to the skillet and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the glace cherry, pickle, thyme, salt, and pepper to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a ramekin and cover with foil.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes, then remove the foil and bake for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the casserole from the oven and let it rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh thyme if desired."
  ],
